00:27:47.220 --> 00:27:51.100
&gt;&gt;Richard: And LeMond you know went into LeMond
and he was just.

00:27:51.100 --> 00:27:52.880
He'd been very hard to pin down initially.

00:27:52.880 --> 00:27:55.650
