Shouldn't he have?

00:49:36.900 --> 00:49:40.420
And even if he's just trying to say the right
thing, and I actually believe he's kind of,

00:49:40.420 --> 00:49:44.809
he's got himself into that mindset where he
actually is immensely proud of finishing second,

00:49:44.809 --> 00:49:49.209
which is, I've never finished second you never
finished second you know It's a rare place

00:49:49.209 --> 00:49:50.209
to be.

